message: Hi Bob, I suggest a 60-40 split in my favor. This is a fair offer considering we both need to reach an agreement, and accepting now means you'll get the full value of your share without any inflation impact.

Alice, I understand the need for a swift resolution. To that end, I'm proposing a 55-45 split in my favor. Accepting this offer now will protect us both from any further uncertainties or inflation impacts, ensuring we each secure our share with no more delays.
